Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:03.69,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}Slowly, quietly, floating by
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.69,0:02:12.40,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,600)}Gently fading into the distant bright sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:21.25,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,600)}More fickle than the wind,\N my goal is beyond it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,0:02:24.37,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}Let's go together
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:30.00,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a breath and skip along,\N the world's spring breath
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:35.60,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun brings all our smiles together
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:43.10,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Between "good morning" and "good bye" it's just us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:46.72,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}We can do whatever we want
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.92,0:02:52.86,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}The sunlight shining down,\N a brand new sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:58.61,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,The morning arch we promised to meet at
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:06.38,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}Waving your hand at me,\N let me make today a special day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:09.54,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,600)}Let's start by talking
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:11.79,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,The chemistry of dreams and the spring wind,\N doesn't feel like it'll stop
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:16.55,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky Happy, gather around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:23.55,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,After always bustling around, what's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:29.10,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but that's why it's exciting
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:31.81,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:39.07,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild, my pace, a master artist during class
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:43.49,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,With a plan in the corner
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:51.04,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Where should we go? Right now is a paradise
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:56.34,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,The unease of being too tightly wound
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:20:03.05,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it late for our date,\N but we got here at the same time
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:08.56,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,This stage of wearing skirts
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:12.48,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how will life be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:20.15,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,The chemistry of dreams and the spring wind, doesn't feel like it'll stop
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:24.78,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky Happy, gather around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:31.95,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,After always bustling around, what's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.95,0:20:37.50,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but that's why it's exciting
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:41.34,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.50,0:22:45.67,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}Next to me in the sunset, a silhouette tall as me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.67,0:22:53.60,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end of another fun day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.47,0:23:01.65,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,I've still got so much unending stuff to talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:08.99,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's time for us to go home
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.99,0:23:16.16,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, see you tomorrow, I'll text you later
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:23.46,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's page is about all our smiles
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:30.76,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, see you tomorrow, thanks as always
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.76,0:23:39.33,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy we could be together today too
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.33,0:23:46.48,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Humhumhum, the wind and my heart are humming
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.48,0:23:53.74,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}At the next corner, I'll turn around and say "Bye bye"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.36,0:00:45.54,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.84,0:00:49.30,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:50.23,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:53.56,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-chan, Yuuko-chan! Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.56,0:00:56.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you just standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:01:00.73,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, look! This was stuck to my forehead!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.73,0:01:02.12,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:03.12,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:05.31,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess that's just like you, Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.31,0:01:07.12,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:09.06,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan, morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.06,0:01:09.89,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.89,0:01:11.30,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:12.09,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.21,0:01:14.23,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Did you watch last night's episode?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.23,0:01:16.84,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yeah! Yeah! It was so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.36,0:01:16.84,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan has a lot of guy friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:18.93,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,She sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.21,0:01:38.90,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tooru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:41.03,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always working so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.85,0:01:43.33,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something up, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.51,0:01:48.83,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:23.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad6\fs90\4a&H74&\pos(914,488)\fad(400,0)\c&HFAECFC&}L{\c&HF7CCFA&}o{\c&HF4B5FD&}v{\c&HEF9AFB&}e
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.91,0:03:28.39,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:30.88,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're as small as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.45,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pet me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:37.20,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you covered in dirt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:38.56,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you fall?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:40.71,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:44.53,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And then, you know what? It was completely flat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:45.74,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has Run been bullying her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.15,0:03:52.70,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was almost hit by a car while chasing a butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.84,0:03:56.34,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got quite a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.23,0:04:02.99,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:04.34,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:08.35,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you at lunch, Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:11.61,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:41.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Run-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:46.26,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru! Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:47.67,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:50.26,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Can I come over now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:52.81,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Come over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.36,0:04:56.61,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. See you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:03.07,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:07.92,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen her since I started studying for the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:22.04,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:26.90,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Tooru-chan! I haven't seen you in ages!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:28.14,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I haven't come by recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:30.84,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run is upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.84,0:05:31.87,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:36.48,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.05,0:06:03.28,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Run-chan will be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:14.68,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:18.93,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got into the same high school as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:25.70,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:34.49,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:35.87,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.17,0:06:37.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.63,0:06:38.54,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:50.39,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:52.17,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Who is this kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.17,0:06:53.85,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan! Who is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:54.93,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:57.75,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got in? Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:06:59.56,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares if I got in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:01.56,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:03.95,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,She really is small!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:05.82,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to introduce us to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:07.82,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Introduce?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:08.99,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:14.74,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might be coming since they posted admissions today, so I called them over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:19.75,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,My friends from school, Yuuko-chan and Nagi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:20.50,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:23.00,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:26.21,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be seeing a lot more of each other in the spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:30.26,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's staring me down like I don't know what...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:32.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You left a pretty bad first impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should explain what you were doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:42.56,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... It's a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:45.06,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run started tickling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:47.15,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We weren't doing anything weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:49.57,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just playing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.55,0:08:00.72,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:13.27,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:16.08,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,200)}Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.14,0:08:13.27,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they're already getting along really well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:16.08,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Shouldn't you stop her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:39.64,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'll pass out the forms for your electives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:42.29,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You filled them out last year. You know the drill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:43.16,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:09:01.71,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,This year's homeroom teacher looks completely irresponsible...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:07.27,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is how you fill out the elective selection forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:10.90,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone have any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:16.93,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,As first year students, you might not have many choices, but you will have more as second and third years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:22.01,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have some bearing on your futures, so think them over carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.01,0:09:26.14,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone has any private questions about them, feel free to ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:49.17,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Run will be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:13.59,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:22.72,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lunch, lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:25.18,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru, let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:29.32,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting ahead of yourself there. Tooru isn't here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.32,0:10:32.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right. Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:37.38,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here, Nagi-chan! That's my Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.38,0:10:40.35,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she... hear her call?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:53.86,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Those squirrel pins are cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:54.85,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:56.47,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're my favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.47,0:10:58.83,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.83,0:11:02.75,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Then what's your favorite animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:04.60,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I like birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:06.75,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, like parakeets?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:08.98,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are pretty cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:10.48,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:17.69,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hair kind of looks like one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:20.97,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they're tasty too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:22.25,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That kind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:25.03,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eating parakeets?! That's so cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:26.53,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.39,0:11:32.67,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan likes chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:34.55,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's what you meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.55,0:11:36.96,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You meant chicken is your favorite thing to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:40.19,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! But I like any kind of meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.19,0:11:42.13,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't we go out for Korean barbecue sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:48.00,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like eating some galbi and dwaeji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:51.19,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I really want to eat some...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:55.32,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can almost hear the sound of meat cooking right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:03.77,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, that was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:05.24,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ringtone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:08.74,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your lunch looks really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:10.36,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind if I take some?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:12.14,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:13.73,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:19.89,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:21.51,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.71,0:12:33.73,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:36.44,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two get along really well, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:39.47,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't look like "getting along"...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:43.09,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a good lunch, right, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:44.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:50.69,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:54.01,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our classroom is over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:57.93,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.\N We were first years until just the other day. Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:12:59.05,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.05,0:13:01.74,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might not make it in time if you don't hurry, Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.74,0:13:04.13,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:28.07,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:07.87,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, you didn't fall asleep this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:10.34,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! I'm fine in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.34,0:14:13.37,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you didn't wake up when you almost fell out the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:15.04,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really need to be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.21,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:20.29,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, I get sleepy after lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:23.48,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then how about some candy to wake you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:24.09,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.96,0:14:28.52,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.03,0:14:37.24,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. One for you too, Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.24,0:14:39.05,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.05,0:14:40.44,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:42.64,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:45.44,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll save it for Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:47.90,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you won't have any, Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:50.64,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll split it in half.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:52.91,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, you're so kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:56.79,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,How will you split that candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:03.75,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know! A cutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:06.60,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I can cut it with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:10.99,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go crazy.\N You'd be an idiot to get hurt over a piece of candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:12.43,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:17.27,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it working?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:31.62,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It fell on the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.62,0:15:33.66,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:36.57,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it would work out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:47.67,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:51.17,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:54.66,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:02.52,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:05.27,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I smell candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:13.53,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I smell candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:15.24,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still have some?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:18.62,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Candy! Candy! Candy! Candy! Candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:17.70,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:21.08,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to throw away the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:26.37,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, Tooru! You can even sniff out empty bags!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.37,0:16:29.24,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru loves sweet things a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.24,0:16:33.13,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. We just ate the last ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:34.79,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring more tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.79,0:16:37.15,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want tortoiseshell candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:40.52,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we make it something not sweet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:42.53,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or something with less calories...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:45.37,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's only candy if it's sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:48.07,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay. I'll bring more tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:53.74,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you pick for your electives?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:55.03,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:57.49,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamade-sensei gave a talk about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:16:59.68,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run was sleeping then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:04.18,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:07.25,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why did you fall over, Yuuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:10.76,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run looked like she would fall over, so I tried to catch her,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:13.99,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,but then Run stopped and I lost my balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:19.14,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tooru. What did you choose for your first elective?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:22.12,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.83,0:17:32.33,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to take
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:36.65,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,the same class as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.65,0:17:38.67,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:54.12,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.19,0:18:03.18,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:06.48,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:18.76,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru is just so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.76,0:18:21.16,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.46,0:18:27.75,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tooru. How about we all go for something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:29.04,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:32.92,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No fair, Yuuko! Let me hug her too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:35.13,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's so soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:39.98,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:45.56,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.57,0:20:58.11,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:21:01.65,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run really has a lot of guy friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:03.69,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what they talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.75,0:21:08.82,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us Yuuko-chan's three sizes, Run-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.82,0:21:13.70,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it a secret, okay? From the top: 88, 56, 87.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.70,0:21:15.96,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! That's nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:18.18,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.18,0:21:20.92,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know my sizes, Nagi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:25.72,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later then, Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:26.72,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:28.38,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.71,0:21:29.72,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:32.68,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.67,0:21:40.69,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:42.48,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.54,0:21:45.03,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.21,0:21:50.99,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Working hard as always, huh, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.53,0:21:57.01,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru, I brought candy just as promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:22:00.17,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all have some later.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:09.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.48,0:22:13.88,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two get along really well, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.80,0:22:12.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.13,0:22:23.03,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:56.45,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H9E49D6&\3c&HCACFBF&}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.77,0:23:58.33,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of rain, there are all sorts of different kinds.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.33,0:23:59.70,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drizzle, light rain, tears in rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.70,0:24:01.96,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh wow, you know more than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.96,0:24:03.83,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a question for you, Mihorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.83,0:24:04.58,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.58,0:24:06.56,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, who are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.56,0:24:09.55,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you just told everyone my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.55,0:24:12.76,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear, Yutaka has just failed miserably.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.76,0:24:15.66,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next A Channel: Rainy Days are for Baths.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.66,0:24:19.12,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, if we're doing the preview, then are we appearing next—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.12,0:24:20.68,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a secret.
